{
  "id": "wuxia-letter",
  "name": "武侠密函",
  "category": "wuxia",
  "description": "一封武侠风格的密函，带有江湖气息和武侠元素",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.03,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "武侠|江湖|侠客|门派|武林|剑客",
        "description": "武侠场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "密函标题"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "发送者"
    },
    "recipient": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "接收者"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 400,
      "description": "密函内容"
    },
    "signature": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "署名"
    },
    "urgentLevel": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "紧急",
      "options": ["普通", "紧急", "十万火急"],
      "description": "紧急程度"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一封武侠密函。\n\n背景信息：\n- 发送者：{{sender}}\n- 接收者：{{recipient}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n- 紧急程度：{{urgentLevel}}\n\n要求：\n1. 使用武侠风格的语言，带有江湖气息\n2. 可以包含门派、武功、江湖术语\n3. 语气要豪迈或神秘\n4. 字数控制在150-300字之间\n\n请直接输出密函内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "wuxia",
    "colors": ["#1a1a1a", "#c41e3a", "#f5e6c8"],
    "mood": "江湖豪迈"
  },
  "rarity": "rare",
  "collectible": true
}